source.sqlReaderQuery:
select 
 cast(c.id as nvarchar) as U_PortalID
,c.fSerialNumber
,c.callID
,c.status
,c.dtCreatedDate 
,c.Subject
,c.closeDate
,c.itemName
,c.itemCode
,c.Customer
,c.custmrName
,c.callType
,c.ComplaintSource
,s.servicedate
,s.dtcheckoutdate
,cast(s.status as nvarchar) serviceStatus
,s.fcreatedbyid
,s.UserServiceCenterSAPID
from srv.Mrr_Complaint C
left join srv.Mrr_Service   S on C.fServiceID = S.ID

union all

select 
 U_PortalID
,internalSN
,callid
,status
,U_CompDate
,subject
,closeDate
,itemName
,itemCode
,customer
,custmrName
,callType
,NULL as ComplaintSource
,U_ServiceDate
,U_dtcheckoutdate
,U_ServiceStatus
,cast(userSign as int) userSign
,U_UserServiceCenter
from sap.Mrr_OSCL
